reviews.review_text:
Thanks Mick Matty and Joe B.   What a team! the Transfers you do are miraculous. 
   The show was recorded using 60 min Chrome cassettes, the only tape available to me as I left for the show.
  Clarity was better but the cuts it caused were unfortunate.
  Thanks to these fine men it is now complete .
  I met Fred Fier at this show. He is now a little under the weather....and I hope he is feeling no pain.
   gratefully,  Jimmy Warburton
